    "GRUs are a middle ground between RNNs and LSTMs in terms of the computational cost.",
    "They are designed to capture long-term dependencies more efficiently than RNNs, but with fewer parameters than LSTMs, making them a more computationally efficient alternative to LSTMs in many scenarios."
